{"tid":2039893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"PTGF 扮黃去幫中學生義補 實則想呃錢","createTime":"2020-05-28T08:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T09:47:21.000Z","uid":344999,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bf726c4e0f34261fc9b6324b5633812eddd26e4c","tid":2039893,"uid":344999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T08:58:25.000Z","msg":"PTGF 回帶<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條女淨係得中學畢業<br />\nYear 1 讀咗一個月就quit，仲成日拎住張大學學生證呃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前同saveHK51 合作<br />\n兩邊都係仆街唔怪得咁夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲死人JM tone 英文真係好到幫到人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好誤人子弟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話想幫到啲手足，但係食Starbucks、買VANS、攞民建聯揮春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係真黃定偽黃大家自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢仲好意思大大聲公審人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身都想隻眼開隻眼閉，但係佢依家仲要出埋啲冇頭冇尾嘅POST直接想問手足「籌錢」就真係睇唔過眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸︰唔係想分化或者鬥黃，只係真係睇唔過眼驚有人俾佢呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515108b8554083b4c9629dba0ac730deb94566a9","tid":2039893,"uid":131766,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T09:03:42.000Z","msg":"又鬥黃 係咪想輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9511b9181483848906ef77026764688a6656cc5","tid":2039893,"uid":22138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T09:06:38.000Z","msg":"Thank remind"},{"pid":"d88676a836138edff50a5cb8f12065ee216db290","tid":2039893,"uid":122134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T09:06:54.000Z","msg":"我唔明佢籌錢個story<br />\n懷疑係呃錢個段野係點解<br />\n咩叫比埋佢既bank account同全名<br />\n咁就可以說服到人?"},{"pid":"74947e7997401895e2a285ea83b612f47514277f","tid":2039893,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T09:26:21.000Z","msg":"仲有做ptgf??可以諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"479f4da189b29ef0564630930e0dfc41a62e8db0","tid":2039893,"uid":189109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"74947e7997401895e2a285ea83b612f47514277f","tid":2039893,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T09:26:21.000Z","msg":"仲有做ptgf??可以諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T09:26:59.000Z","msg":"⚠️由于此讯息不符合国家安全法规，已被屏蔽。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad3175ca92d6194b4950c87b448c6094d504102","tid":2039893,"uid":18114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T09:34:18.000Z","msg":"我想睇PTGF 果part 黃唔黃是但啦 反正咁多人呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重點係有冇閃卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid